title.rendered: BOSS AIR AIRBAG 2401 SINGLE BELLOW COMPLETE

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR AIRBAG 2401 SINGLE BELLOW COMPLETE

Boss Air Airbag 2401 Single Bellow Complete available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This product has a 2400lb capacity @ 100psi Government approved Tested to over 750psi Suitable for “Bag over” applications and as a stand alone air bag in Automotive suspensions.

Includes:

  • 2400lb Extreme Series Bag
  • Top and Bottom plate and stainless bolts.
  • 12 countersunk stainless bolts

Fully Compressed – 65mm with 6mm ends fitted
Max Diameter- 135mm (widest when fully compressed)
Max height – 110mm
Max working pressure 0-160psi
Test pressure – 480psi
Burst pressure – 750psi

CLICK HERE to view the range of Boss Air products available!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
